name: 30 Degree Tree
description:
You are a cat that accidentally, unintentionally, and unknowingly step on a branch of the last highest tree in the world, making it unbalance and unstable. Balance the tree and keep it from falling!

Controls:

You can move left, right, and jump. with what key? anything! well the default setting is:

Move LeftAMove Right
DJumpW
